    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1176370395">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1176370395" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1176370395" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1176370395">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3314793/">二云三英</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">需精读。条理非常清晰，重点非常突出，就把狭义封建制这个概念讲透，读起来有种莫名的爽快感，不愧名著。期待接下来读布洛赫的《封建社会》。就是装帧不好，封面边缘容易磨掉色。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1136018133">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
